      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 16,
      "message": "Because the swagger.json is generated by a unit test that starts the REST server, issues the REST request to read the swagger.json, and then saves the swagger.json file to target/swagger/swagger.json.\n\nThe other plugins need the swagger.json to run, so if unit tests are not executed, the swagger.json file is not there and the plugin execution fails.",
